            "draft_value": "* NASA's Science Mission Directorate (SMD) manages a portfolio of over 100 missions exploring our Earth, Sun, solar system, and the universe.\n* Executes scientific priorities established by the National Academies' peer-reviewed Decadal Surveys to ensure nonpartisan discovery.\n* Advances U.S. leadership in space through robotic exploration, weather forecasting, and planetary defense.\n* Supports a national network of researchers, engineers, and private-sector partners to maintain American preeminence in STEM.",
